{"tid":1410722,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"八號風球 催淚彈 sorry你都要開舖","createTime":"2019-08-05T02:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:45:13.000Z","uid":187578,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"89e45b85332f1383f1991f49cc04df2672bd91fe","tid":1410722,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:19:19.000Z","msg":"［代友post］<br />\n<br />\n喺<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">優x良品</span></span>返工<br />\n平時8號風球都要照返工同埋冇得放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只有十號風球先可以走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實都好想知有冇違反勞工條例？<br />\n<br />\n大家都知<span style=\"color: red;\">8月3號</span>，旺角同埋尖沙咀好多店都唔開甚至關門<br />\n但我地公司就<span style=\"color: red;\">一直都唔比關門</span>，經理只係叫我地自己留意出面情況，唔打到埋泥都唔比走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出面放幾多催淚彈、胡椒噴霧、就算開槍都<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你死你事<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日8月5罷工，交通工具死晒，但唔理你，你都要照返～<br />\n<br />\n大家都知，其實我地店係做遊客生意<br />\n講真 又遊行點會有咩生意<br />\n但sorry呀 你死你事 公司唔會理你嫁<br />\n<br />\n呢間店多數都師奶做唔識啲咩，唔返一日都扣成幾千花紅～但老闆完全冷血無良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認真奉勸大家想搵工嘅千其唔好入泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />祝你地早啲執笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6fcce8bc87547507b4ff5cea5bbfa606dd5fe1","tid":1410722,"uid":122031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:32:57.000Z","msg":"邊個會買 都唔撚抵"},{"pid":"30e874081b3e9910f6acda66b45b02535579beea","tid":1410722,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d6fcce8bc87547507b4ff5cea5bbfa606dd5fe1","tid":1410722,"uid":122031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:32:57.000Z","msg":"邊個會買 都唔撚抵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:34:3